 Earth AI</a><span>, a Not Boring Capital portfolio company that is explori=
ng and drilling for critical metals. Its AI model predicts the location of =
deposits, and its drilling platform verifies them 4x faster and 4x more che=
aply. It&#8217;s a killer combo: the company has already made three discove=
ries when a traditional explorer is successful if it makes just one. </span=
></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px=
; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">In that piece, I mentioned another mining startup, K=
